N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 62.5 - Definition of sewage

State Regulations

For the purpose of this Part the term "sewage" shall have
the same meaning as that defined in subdivision (d) of section 1202 of the

Public Health Law. Notes
